2ee8dbc957b22c123c3116ab7540a28c01fcab2664a2fa9707aabdaeff952900e96f7b8121338acfea2c2bd5a0b806f61835e2bcd8e3f17ed757841587365b0f  0001-Use-qmlplugindump-qt5.patch
"
